WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:08.000
This is your RestoreAssist Dashboard.

00:08.000 --> 00:16.000
The Overview section shows active jobs, upcoming inspections, team status, and pending claims.

00:16.000 --> 00:24.000
Navigation is simple — use the sidebar to jump to any module, the search bar to find anything, or quick action buttons for common tasks.

00:24.000 --> 00:32.000
The Insights panel shows job completion rates, your workspace health score, and recent activity.

00:32.000 --> 00:40.000
Everything you need to run your restoration business, in one place.